y Murders: Anniversary Of Roadside Shooting That Claimed 4 Lives|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2012/12/15/alberta-highway-murders-anniversary_n_2308158.html|website=Huffpost Alberta|publisher=The Huffington Post|accessdate=July 5, 2016|date=December 15, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Eaton centre shooting|Eaton Centre Shooting]]\n|June 2, 2012\n|[[Toronto|Toronto, Ontario]]\n|2\n| \n| No\n|Gang member open fires in the mall food court as an act of revenge for a former stabbing, killing 2 and injuring 6 others.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/christopher-husbands-eaton-centre-shooter-testifies-1.4953465|title=Defence argues Eaton Centre shooter was suffering from PTSD {{!}} CBC News|last=Dec 19|first=Jasmin Seputis \u00b7 Posted|last2=December 20|first2=2018 10:38 PM ET {{!}} Last Updated|website=CBC|language=en|access-date=2019-02-10|last3=2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Danzig Street shooting]]\n|July 16, 2012\n|[[Scarborough, Toronto|Scarborough]], [[Toronto]], [[Ontario]]\n|2\n| Hand gun\n| No\n|Mass gang shooting at a block party that left 2 dead and 23 injured.<ref name=\"RushCharges\">{{cite news\n|last1= Rush\n|first1= Curtis\n|last2= Poisson\n|first2= Jayme\n|last3= Powell\n|first3= Betsy\n|date= November 8, 2012\n|title= Danzig St. shooting: First-degree murder charges laid in July shootings\n|url= https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2012/11/08/danzig_st_shooting_firstdegree_murder_charges_laid_in_july_shootings.html\n|work= Toronto Star\n|publisher= Toronto Star Newspapers Limited\n|accessdate= June 4, 2017\n|url-status= live\n|archive-url= https://archive.today/20180227162458/https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2012/11/08/danzig_st_shooting_firstdegree_murder_charges_laid_in_july_shootings.html\n|archivedate= February 27, 2018\n}}</ref>\n|-\n|Les Racines de vie Montessori\n|April 5, 2013\n|[[Gatineau, Quebec]]\n| 2\n| Hand gun\n| Yes\n|** Not a massacre by the definition shown at beginning of article.  School Shooting.  Daycare worker killed, shooter co